item.title: Monster spawnning help
item.dc:creator: @nitrdude150 nitrdude150
item.description:
@nitrdude150 wrote:

::spawn (npcid) is to spawn it, but you cant attack it, you can autospawn them in autospawn.cfg, just put the npc id and the coords, to get coords just type in ::mypos, and thats it. If you have any more questions,
